"&oldreleasename; system to another hard disk or partition, and then upgrade "
"only one of the two copies. You can then use <prgn>chroot</prgn> to run the "
"&oldreleasename; version in parallel to the &releasename; version."
msgstr ""

# type: <p></p>
#: ../en/release-notes.en.sgml:2775
msgid ""
"It is not possible to have the old and new versions of Zope/Plone installed "
"together on an &releasename; system, partly because the old packages depend "
"on <package>python2.3</package> which cannot be installed together with "
"<package>python2.4</package>."
